ygData.messageBody:
Actually, Nagafen was slained last night on Solusek Ro as well... I wasnt
there but a gm did a broadcast of the event, and i did a /who all 50 and the
list was cut short as so many on at the time, but most of the names were in
Solusek B. wish i woulda seen it

Minkin Nehoc
Solusek Ro
